# Design Council Double Diamond 雙鑽石模型官方定義 Discover Define Develop Deliver 四階段標準用法：雙鑽石 Double Diamond 官方定義 經典用法 vs 個人問題到商業化兩階段套用

## 來源列表
1. [Framework for Innovation - Design Council](https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/framework-for-innovation/) — 頁面未標示發布日期；頁尾 © 2026
2. [The Double Diamond - Design Council](https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/the-double-diamond/) — 頁面未標示發布日期；頁尾 © 2026
3. [History of the Double Diamond - Design Council](https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/the-double-diamond/history-of-the-double-diamond/) — 頁面未標示發布日期；頁尾 © 2026
4. [Iconic design process ‘The Double Diamond’ turns 20 - Design Council PDF](https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/fileadmin/uploads/dc/Documents/Press_Releases/The_Double_Diamond_turns_20_-_9_May_2023_Final.pdf) — 4 May 2023
5. [Double Diamond Model: The Design Process Framework Explained - Dovetail](https://dovetail.com/design-thinking/double-diamond-model/) — Last updated 15 April 2026

## 原文摘錄

### 來源 1
> “a clear, comprehensive and visual description of the design process”

URL: https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/framework-for-innovation/

### 來源 2
> “A universally accepted depiction of the design process.”

URL: https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/the-double-diamond/

### 來源 3
> “named Discover, Define, Develop and Deliver”

URL: https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/resources/the-double-diamond/history-of-the-double-diamond/

### 來源 4
> “through 4 keys steps (Discover, Define, Develop and Deliver)”

URL: https://www.designcouncil.org.uk/fileadmin/uploads/dc/Documents/Press_Releases/The_Double_Diamond_turns_20_-_9_May_2023_Final.pdf

### 來源 5
> “maps how designers move from understanding a problem to delivering a solution”

URL: https://dovetail.com/design-thinking/double-diamond-model/

## 關鍵重點
- Design Council 官方把 Double Diamond 定義為「設計流程」的視覺化描述，不是單一工具或固定表單。（來源 1、2）
- 官方標準四階段是 Discover、Define、Develop、Deliver。（來源 3、4）
- 官方 Framework for Innovation 說明兩個 diamond 對應 divergent thinking 與 convergent thinking：先廣泛探索問題，再聚焦行動。（來源 1）
- Discover / Define 屬於釐清問題；Develop / Deliver 屬於提出、測試、收斂解法。（來源 1、3、4）
- 官方明確說它不是線性流程，測試與學習可能讓團隊回到前面階段。（來源 1、2）
- Dovetail 2026 文章代表近期產品／研究語境的標準解讀：Double Diamond 是從理解問題到交付解法的流程框架。（來源 5）

## 不確定點
- 「個人問題到商業化兩階段套用」在本次查到的 Design Council 官方資料中無資料；官方資料只明確支援「problem to solution」與 Discover / Define / Develop / Deliver 四階段。
- Design Council 官方頁面本身未標示清楚發布日期；只能確認頁面仍在 2026 官網資源區，另有 2023 年 20 週年新聞稿作為具日期來源。
